{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_05_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 星の海の中で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、もしかして緊張してますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ are you nervous by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんしてるわよ\nデビューして以来、ずっとライブ前は緊張しているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I am.\nEver since my debut‚ I've been nervous before every live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブは一期一会だもの。同じステージは二度とない\nだから、緊張感は忘れたくないってずっと思ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each live is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. The same stage won't come again.\nThat's why I always want to keep that sense of tension.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いつか、麻奈も同じようなことを言ってました\n似てるのかもしれませんね、莉央さんと麻奈は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mana used to say something similar too.\nMaybe you and Mana are similar in that sense‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。ステージに対する気持ちは同じ\n……と、言いたいけど、そうでもないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Our feelings toward the stage are the same.\n…Well‚ that's what I want to say‚ but it's not entirely true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あの子は最後までステージに立ち続けたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She continued to stand on the stage until the end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私は一度、ステージを降りた人間だもの\n彼女がいなくなって、アイドルを辞めかけたことがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I once stepped off the stage.\nWhen she was gone‚ there was a time I considered quitting being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "良かったです。戻って来てくれて\nもし莉央さんが辞めたら、麻奈は悲しんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad you came back.\nIf you were to quit‚ I think Mana would be really sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そうかしら？　あの子だったら\n悲しむっていうよりも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? With her‚ maybe…\nRather than being sad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "なんで辞めるのよーって\n怒って化けて出そうじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She'd more likely say‚ \"Why are you quitting?!\"\nShe might get mad and show her true colors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうかも……いえ、きっとそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be true… No‚ I'm sure it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃はグランプリの決勝で、麻奈に会ったような\n感覚があったと言っていたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono said she had a feeling that\nshe met Mana at the Grand Prix finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "貴方も、そんな風に感じることはあったのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you ever feel anything similar?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ。ありましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、私も今日、会えるかしら？\nあの子の歌を歌えば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. I wonder if I'll be able to see her today.\nIf I sing her song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "会えますよ。きっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll be able to. Definitely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだといいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈に会ったら、伝えたいことはありますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you meet Mana‚ is there something you'd like to tell her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……いろいろあるけど、貴方には内緒",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… there are many things‚ but I'll keep them a secret from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "また内緒ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Another secret?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "女同士の話に首をつっこむのは無粋よ\n……じゃあ、行って来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not polite to pry into women's conversations.\n…Well then‚ I'll be off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はい、琴乃との共演、楽しみにしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ looking forward to performing with Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 117.6
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……終わったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、私と琴乃の『星の海の記憶』\nうまく歌えていたかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ how well did we sing \"Memories of the Starry Sea‚\" me and Kotono?\nDid it turn out well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、その薄い反応は……\nえ？　貴方……もしかして泣いていたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with that faint reaction…\nEh? You… were you crying‚ by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、そんなことは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it's nothing like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そういうことにしておくわ\n貴方にそこまで響いたのなら、合格点かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ let's just leave it at that.\nIf it touched you that deeply‚ I guess that's a passing grade.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "本当に泣いてませんからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really wasn't crying‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "まぁいいわ。どちらにしろ貴方、強くなったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh well. Either way‚ you've become stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "出会った頃の貴方は、絶対こっちの世界では\nやってけない人って思っていたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I met you at first‚ I thought you were\nsomeone who couldn't make it in this world.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "……みんな少しずつ成長して、大人になっていくのね\n立ち止まることは出来ない。前に進むしかないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you've grown‚ little by little‚ and become an adult.\nThere's no stopping‚ we have to keep moving forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "私は、いなくなったあの子に\n置いて行かれた気持ちになっていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I used to feel left behind by\nthat girl who disappeared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "本当は私達が、彼女を置いて行っているのかも\n……なんだか寂しいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in truth‚ it might be us who left her behind.\n…It's a bit lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈は、それでいいって言うと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mana would probably say that it's okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思う。あの子ならきっと\n感傷に浸ってる私達の背中を蹴っ飛ばすでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She'd likely kick us in the back and\ntell us to stop indulging in sentimentality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央さん。ステージの上で、麻奈に会えましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio-san. Did you meet Mana on stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "会えたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……なら、良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In that case‚ I'm relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "貴方のことも、少しだけ伝えたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her a bit about you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "なんて伝えたのかは、やっぱり秘密ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it still a secret what you told her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、もちろんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "ここから見上げる星、綺麗ね。海に映る星も\n……本当に、星の海みたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The stars we see from here‚ they're so beautiful.\nThe stars reflected in the sea are beautiful too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "今、こうして貴方と見ているこの海を\n私はきっと、一生忘れない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's really like a sea of stars.\nThis sea I'm looking at with you now‚ I'm sure I'll never forget it in my life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_03-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈が、綺麗だと感じた、この星の海を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This sea of stars‚ where Mana felt it was beautiful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}